snippet.title: Burn Zombie Burn HD video game trailer - PC Mac PS3
snippet.description:
http://gamezplay.org  - The crypt keepers at Pinnacle Software and developer Doublesix have today lifted the lid on a brand new in-game trailer and screenshots which reveals all of the enemy zombie types players will encounter in the fiendishly addictive arcade shooter Burn Zombie Burn!, releasing on PlayStation Network.
More at www.gamezplay.org
